content.rendered:
The Azumi Desk Screen is a perfect complement to our brilliant Azumi range of desks.

Available from stock in a range of colours & finishes but can be made to order in your specific fabric requirements (POA).

Easy to assemble and aid privacy & sound blocking. Held in stock for delivery 2-3 working days as standard.
